<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Wilhelm von Rechberg zu Hohenrechberg, Amtmann zu Uffenheim</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Eberhard Has, Diener der Stadt, wegen der im Geleit des Adressaten beschlagnahmten Habe Nürnberger Kaufleute an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_394" id="196r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_394_r1l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> VVılhelm von Rehberg cʒu <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Rechb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r1l17">Amptman cʒu vffenheym </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_394_r1l18">Edler vnd lıeber her wilhelm / Als vnſer lıeber Burger </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r1l19">vnd Ratgeſelle 
<del rend="strikethrough">n </del> <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Ebner 
<del rend="strikethrough"> b </del> mit euch geredt vnd auſʒ - </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r1l20">getragen hat von des geleits wegen etc Alſo iſt vns <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r1l21">vvie man den ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>yecʒund<ex>en</ex></expan> in dem geleyte do Jr dann </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r1l22">cʒugeleyten habt etwieuil hab vnd <expan>kauffmanſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> hab </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r1l23">darümb ſenden vvir cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> haſen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r1l24">mit euch dauon ʒu reden vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> . vvaʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> vnſer <expan>dyen<ex>er</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_394_r1l25"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> valentini </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_394" id="196r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Wilhelm von Rehberg czu
                                                  <expan>Ob<ex>er</ex>n</expan><expan>rechb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>,
                                                amptman czu Uffenheym</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edler und lieber her Wilhelm, als unser lieber burger und ratgeselle
                <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> Ebner mit euch geredt und auszgetragen hat von des
            geleits wegen etc., also ist uns <expan>fürkume<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie man den
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>yeczund<ex>en</ex></expan> in dem geleyte, do ir dann czu geleyten habt, etwievil
            hab und <expan>kauffmans<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> hab; darümb senden wir czu
              <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edell <expan>Eb<ex>erhart</ex></expan> Hasen,
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dyener, mit euch davon zu reden. Und
                <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> unser
                <expan>dyen<ex>er</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>do<ex>min</ex>ica</expan>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Valentini.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
